trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart" />, an <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding" /> or an <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding" />.
trans-unit.target: Representa un elemento de extensibilidad agregado a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart" />, a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding" /> o a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding" />.

trans-unit.source: It specifies the schema for XML messages that are not SOAP compliant.
trans-unit.target: Especifica el esquema para los mensajes XML que no son compatibles con SOAP.

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información acerca de cómo especificar protocolos de servicios Web XML, vea [ [ \<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices >]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información acerca de lenguaje de descripción de servicios Web (WSDL), vea la especificación en http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates a typical use of the `MimeXmlBinding` class.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo siguiente se muestra un uso típico de la `MimeXmlBinding` clase.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> to which the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding" /> applies.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece el nombre del objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> al que se aplica <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding" />.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: El valor predeterminado es una cadena vacía ("").
